#: ../../developer/code/code-signing.rst:6 256022aaa3fa47de9c794bf1b1ecc35a
msgid ""
"All contributions to the Qubes OS :doc:`source code </developer/code"
"/source-code>` must be cryptographically signed by the author’s PGP key."
msgstr ""

