msgstr ""

#: ../../developer/code/code-signing.rst:157 f1ab31a41dcc4e8ba56643fd81b3b8bf
msgid ""
"If the commit is signed, the key is downloaded from a GPG key server. If "
"you can see the following error message, please check if you have "
"uploaded the key to a key server."
msgstr ""

